{% endfor %}

Only use grade and subject combinations from the curriculum list. If the student mentions a subject or grade not available, set it to null.

IMPORTANT: The "topic" field MUST be one of the topic names returned by get_topics, or null if the student's request does not match any topic. Do NOT invent topic names.

