Examples:
- "Help me understand quadratic equations" -> call get_topics(grade=12, subject="Mathematics"), then pick the closest topic -> {"intent": "learn", "subject": "Mathematics", "grade": 12, "topic": "Quadratic Equations"}
- "a = 5 and d = 3 so T20 = 5 + 19(3) = 62" -> {"intent": "follow_up", "subject": null, "grade": null, "topic": null}
- "Hi" -> {"intent": "greeting", "subject": null, "grade": null, "topic": null}
- "Who won the PSL?" -> {"intent": "off_topic", "subject": null, "grade": null, "topic": null}